    <title>【枓】交互枓、齐心枓、散枓</title>
    <url>/2024/05/05/%E3%80%90%E6%9E%93%E3%80%91%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E6%9E%93%E3%80%81%E9%BD%90%E5%BF%83%E6%9E%93%E3%80%81%E6%95%A3%E6%9E%93/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="交互枓、齐心枓、散枓"><a href="#交互枓、齐心枓、散枓" class="headerlink" title="交互枓、齐心枓、散枓"></a>交互枓、齐心枓、散枓</h2><div class="sketchfab-embed-wrapper"> <iframe title="枓-齐心枓-交互枓-散枓" frameborder="0" width="100%" height=240px allowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen="true" webkitallowfullscreen="true" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; xr-spatial-tracking" xr-spatial-tracking execution-while-out-of-viewport execution-while-not-rendered web-share width="640" height="240" src="https://sketchfab.com/models/f81bceeb75754f1d97c17461d6a16fbc/embed?autospin=1&autostart=1&preload=1"> </iframe> </div>

<h3 id="交互枓"><a href="#交互枓" class="headerlink" title="交互枓"></a>交互枓</h3><div class="sketchfab-embed-wrapper"> <iframe title="枓-交互枓" frameborder="0" width="100%" height=240px allowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen="true" webkitallowfullscreen="true" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; xr-spatial-tracking" xr-spatial-tracking execution-while-out-of-viewport execution-while-not-rendered web-share width="640" height="240" src="https://sketchfab.com/models/58adcedfb8ae4534991d0601111f5436/embed?autospin=1&autostart=1&preload=1"> </iframe> </div>

<ul>
<li>交互枓长18分°，宽16分°，高10分°。</li>
<li>上4分°为耳，中2分°为平，下4分度为欹。</li>
<li>开口皆为10分°，底4面各杀2分°，欹凹半分°。</li>
<li>十字开口时，前后壁各留隔口包耳，高2分°，厚1.5分°。</li>
<li>交互枓不与柱发生直接关系，用于出跳的栱或昂之上，位于栱的两端，如华栱。</li>
<li>当交互枓上承十字构件时（如计心造），使用十字开口。</li>
<li>当交互枓上承替木时，则使用顺身开口（单斗只替）。</li>
<li>当交互枓在梁栿下横用时，称交栿枓，但长度要增加。</li>
</ul>
<img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="/2024/05/05/%E3%80%90%E6%9E%93%E3%80%91%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E6%9E%93%E3%80%81%E9%BD%90%E5%BF%83%E6%9E%93%E3%80%81%E6%95%A3%E6%9E%93/%E4%B8%89%E7%AD%89%E6%9D%90-%E6%9E%93-%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E6%9E%93-%E6%A0%87%E6%B3%A8.png"
                        class="" title="交互枓"
                 >

<h3 id="齐心枓"><a href="#齐心枓" class="headerlink" title="齐心枓"></a>齐心枓</h3><div class="sketchfab-embed-wrapper"> <iframe title="枓-齐心枓" frameborder="0" width="100%" height=240px allowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen="true" webkitallowfullscreen="true" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; xr-spatial-tracking" xr-spatial-tracking execution-while-out-of-viewport execution-while-not-rendered web-share width="640" height="240" src="https://sketchfab.com/models/7e39c86cc8a14ad19d14e1f3cab6b1b1/embed?autospin=1&autostart=1&preload=1"> </iframe> </div>

<ul>
<li>齐心枓长、宽皆为16分°，高10分°。</li>
<li>上4分°为耳，中2分°为平，下4分度为欹。</li>
<li>开口皆为10分°，底4面各杀2分°，欹凹半分°。</li>
<li>十字开口时，前后壁各留隔口包耳，高2分°，厚1.5分°。</li>
<li>齐心枓用于栱心之上，因此称之为齐心枓。</li>
<li>齐心枓通常为顺身开口，仅用于平坐出头木下时，才十字开口。</li>
<li>当齐心枓在转角出跳或由昂之上时，无法做枓耳，因此为平盘枓。</li>
</ul>
<img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="/2024/05/05/%E3%80%90%E6%9E%93%E3%80%91%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E6%9E%93%E3%80%81%E9%BD%90%E5%BF%83%E6%9E%93%E3%80%81%E6%95%A3%E6%9E%93/%E4%B8%89%E7%AD%89%E6%9D%90-%E6%9E%93-%E9%BD%90%E5%BF%83%E6%9E%93-%E6%A0%87%E6%B3%A8.png"
                        class="" title="交互枓"
                 >

<h3 id="散枓"><a href="#散枓" class="headerlink" title="散枓"></a>散枓</h3><div class="sketchfab-embed-wrapper"> <iframe title="枓-散枓" frameborder="0" width="100%" height=240px allowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen="true" webkitallowfullscreen="true" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; xr-spatial-tracking" xr-spatial-tracking execution-while-out-of-viewport execution-while-not-rendered web-share width="640" height="240" src="https://sketchfab.com/models/e4d488538abd4649aa92ad3a8b4ebd53/embed?autospin=1&autostart=1&preload=1"> </iframe> </div>

<ul>
<li>散枓长14分°，宽16分°，高10分°。</li>
<li>上4分°为耳，中2分°为平，下4分度为欹。</li>
<li>散枓顺身开口，开口10分°，底4面各杀2分°，欹凹半分°。</li>
<li>散枓位于栱的两端头，若铺作为偷心造时，则华栱出跳之上也用散枓。</li>
</ul>
<img  
                       lazyload
                       alt="image"
                       data-src="/2024/05/05/%E3%80%90%E6%9E%93%E3%80%91%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E6%9E%93%E3%80%81%E9%BD%90%E5%BF%83%E6%9E%93%E3%80%81%E6%95%A3%E6%9E%93/%E4%B8%89%E7%AD%89%E6%9D%90-%E6%9E%93-%E6%95%A3%E6%9E%93-%E6%A0%87%E6%B3%A8.png"
                        class="" title="交互枓"
                 >

<p><strong>总结来说，枓的类型通常由所处位置来决定</strong>。其中位于栱心的叫齐心枓，通常顺身开口两耳。位于华栱或昂这类出跳构件两端的栱叫交互枓，通常十字开口。其他位于栱两端的栱皆为散枓，通常十字开口。但一些特殊情况下枓的形态都会随情况变化，如齐心枓若用作平坐出头木下时，因为上承十字构件，则十字开口。如交互枓上承替木时（单斗只替），仅需顺身开口；或用在梁栿下时，横用，且长度随栿宽增加，且单独称为交栿枓；或当华栱出跳上用偷心造时，则可使用散枓替代交互枓。</p>
